{"nodes": [{"type": "text", "id": "95479890e769475b", "x": 0, "y": -440, "width": 1430, "height": 110, "color": "6", "text": "# Claude \u5168\u5bb6\u6876\u4e09\u5de5\u5177\u5206\u5de5\n*Anthropic \u628a AI \u80fd\u529b\u5206\u4e09\u5c64,\u5c0d\u61c9 Claude \u4e09\u500b\u7522\u54c1\u7dda*"}, {"type": "text", "id": "2be91bc877c94e8b", "x": 0, "y": -280, "width": 460, "height": 200, "color": "5", "text": "## Claude (Chat)\n**24/7 \u5404\u9818\u57df\u9867\u554f**\n\n\u5beb\u4fe1 / \u6539\u5c65\u6b77 / \u6574\u7406\u6703\u8b70\n\u624b\u6a5f App \u76f4\u63a5\u958b\n*\u96f6\u8a2d\u5b9a / \u96f6\u9580\u6abb*\n"}, {"type": "text", "id": "f2f0019d82884882", "x": 485, "y": -280, "width": 460, "height": 200, "color": "4", "text": "## Claude Cowork\n**\u5b8c\u6574\u6a94\u6848\u7522\u51fa**\n\n\u4e0a\u50b3\u6574\u500b\u8cc7\u6599\u593e / \u9023 Gmail / Notion\n\u8dd1\u7814\u7a76 / \u6574\u7406\u8a2a\u8ac7 / \u81ea\u52d5\u5beb\u6708\u5831\n*\u8de8\u5de5\u5177\u7684\u77e5\u8b58\u5de5\u4f5c*\n"}, {"type": "text", "id": "0d0f90908e9f4235", "x": 970, "y": -280, "width": 460, "height": 200, "color": "3", "text": "## Claude Code\n**Agentic Coding**\n\nTerminal \u5167\u5c0d\u8a71\u64cd\u4f5c\n\u505a\u7db2\u7ad9 / \u5beb\u5de5\u5177 / \u81ea\u52d5\u5316 Excel\n*\u4e0d\u6703\u5beb\u7a0b\u5f0f\u4e5f\u80fd\u7528*\n"}, {"type": "text", "id": "e1860b8e6ef24037", "x": 115, "y": -40, "width": 1200, "height": 160, "color": "6", "text": "## Claude \u5168\u5bb6\u6876\n\n**\u4e00\u500b\u5e95\u5c64\u667a\u80fd,\u4e09\u7a2e\u5de5\u4f5c\u74b0\u5883**\n\n> AI \u4e0d\u662f\u5de5\u5177\u5806\u758a,\u662f\u7d44\u7e54\u7d50\u69cb\u7684\u4e00\u90e8\u5206\n"}, {"type": "text", "id": "139d7fa097984723", "x": 0, "y": 160, "width": 702, "height": 300, "color": "#475569", "text": "## \u4e00\u822c\u4eba\u7684\u4e09\u5c64\u7528\u6cd5\n\n==\u4e0a\u73ed\u65cf== \u2014 Chat \u6539\u4fe1 / Cowork \u8dd1\u6708\u5831\n\n==\u63a5\u6848\u8005== \u2014 Cowork \u5beb\u63d0\u6848 / Code \u84cb\u5ba2\u6236\u7db2\u7ad9\n\n==\u5275\u696d\u8005== \u2014 \u4e09\u5de5\u5177\u540c\u6642\u8dd1\u9a57\u8b49/\u5efa\u7f6e/\u71df\u904b\n"}, {"type": "text", "id": "e094f4a07ba446bc", "x": 727, "y": 160, "width": 702, "height": 300, "color": "1", "text": "## \u26a0\ufe0f \u4e09\u500b\u5e38\u898b\u8e29\u96f7\n\n1. \u53ea\u628a Claude \u7576 ChatGPT \u66ff\u4ee3\u54c1 \u2192 \u6c92\u7528\u5230 Cowork / Code\n2. \u6c92\u5beb\u67b6\u69cb\u8a18\u61b6\u6587\u4ef6 \u2192 \u6bcf\u6b21 session \u91cd\u89e3\u91cb\n3. AI \u5beb code \u76f4\u63a5\u4e0a production \u2192 \u8df3\u904e\u5b89\u5168\u5be9\u67e5\n"}], "edges": [{"id": "de2934a5cff04f2f", "fromNode": "2be91bc877c94e8b", "fromSide": "bottom", "fromEnd": null, "toNode": "e1860b8e6ef24037", "toSide": "top", "toEnd": "none", "color": "#94a3b8", "label": null}, {"id": "6e2a0f5bcc014e87", "fromNode": "f2f0019d82884882", "fromSide": "bottom", "fromEnd": null, "toNode": "e1860b8e6ef24037", "toSide": "top", "toEnd": "none", "color": "#94a3b8", "label": null}, {"id": "eab28f9378224e4e", "fromNode": "0d0f90908e9f4235", "fromSide": "bottom", "fromEnd": null, "toNode": "e1860b8e6ef24037", "toSide": "top", "toEnd": "none", "color": "#94a3b8", "label": null}, {"id": "200a8e87cee649c4", "fromNode": "e1860b8e6ef24037", "fromSide": "bottom", "fromEnd": null, "toNode": "139d7fa097984723", "toSide": "top", "toEnd": "arrow", "color": "6", "label": "*\u843d\u5730*"}, {"id": "bd2c25ad511443ec", "fromNode": "e1860b8e6ef24037", "fromSide": "bottom", "fromEnd": null, "toNode": "e094f4a07ba446bc", "toSide": "top", "toEnd": "arrow", "color": "1", "label": "**\u8b66\u9234**"}]}